1
00:00:00,340 --> 00:00:01,840
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,840 --> 00:00:03,480
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,540 --> 00:00:05,610
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:07,050 --> 00:00:08,310
If I ask for something.

5
00:00:08,880 --> 00:00:09,880
will you do it...

6
00:00:11,020 --> 00:00:12,320
no matter what?

7
00:00:13,120 --> 00:00:18,090
Yes, of course.
Just tell me what it is you want.

8
00:00:19,260 --> 00:00:20,260
Then,

9
00:00:22,260 --> 00:00:23,500
marry me.

10
00:00:26,630 --> 00:00:30,170
I want to become your legal wife.

11
00:00:32,670 --> 00:00:36,470
Wait, a marriage?
Become my legal wife?

12
00:00:38,010 --> 00:00:41,150
Have you lost your mind?

13
00:00:41,510 --> 00:00:42,510
See?

14
00:00:43,780 --> 00:00:46,280
You can't give me what I want.

15
00:00:46,350 --> 00:00:48,450
That's why I'm leaving with Min Jun.

16
00:00:48,720 --> 00:00:52,360
Hold on, wait. Okay, fine.

17
00:00:52,790 --> 00:00:54,160
I understand how you feel.

18
00:00:55,190 --> 00:00:58,560
Min Jun nearly died
and even lost his memories.

19
00:00:59,230 --> 00:01:02,330
With all this talk of his dismissal,
you must be frustrated.

20
00:01:02,670 --> 00:01:04,870
But still,
making a demand like this...

21
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:07,140
out of nowhere?

22
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:08,740
It's not like you.

23
00:01:09,140 --> 00:01:10,140
I'm...

24
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:13,750
a woman too, sir.

25
00:01:17,720 --> 00:01:18,950
For Min Jun's sake,

26
00:01:20,150 --> 00:01:22,620
I gave up my own life as one.

27
00:01:24,420 --> 00:01:26,620
If this is all I get
for that sacrifice,

28
00:01:27,830 --> 00:01:29,630
if I can't even protect Min Jun,

29
00:01:31,660 --> 00:01:35,100
then it's time
I take my own life back.

30
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:37,770
Instead of being your woman,

31
00:01:39,340 --> 00:01:41,710
I'll be another man's wife now.

32
00:01:43,070 --> 00:01:44,810
I'm going to find
a trustworthy man...

33
00:01:46,180 --> 00:01:48,010
and start a completely new life.

34
00:01:51,420 --> 00:01:52,980
You'll be another man's wife?

35
00:01:54,250 --> 00:01:55,650
A new life?

36
00:01:59,020 --> 00:02:00,490
For the past 30 years,

37
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:04,460
I've been by your side.

38
00:02:07,370 --> 00:02:09,170
But it was a relationship
that could end so easily...

39
00:02:11,140 --> 00:02:12,570
with just one packed bag.

40
00:02:14,140 --> 00:02:15,810
It took me way too long
to realize it.

41
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:20,850
Hey, wait. Hold on!

42
00:02:21,350 --> 00:02:24,320
Hear me out.
I don't know about marriage,

43
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:26,220
but I'll make sure
Min Jun's position is secure.

44
00:02:28,790 --> 00:02:31,760
As long as I'm around,
no one will dare...

45
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:34,290
force my son out.

46
00:02:34,290 --> 00:02:35,990
Even if you dismiss the board today,

47
00:02:36,290 --> 00:02:37,330
what about next time?

48
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:43,770
Your wife will keep tormenting him,
preying on his memory loss.

49
00:02:43,870 --> 00:02:45,000
Come on.

50
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:49,310
Are you saying that I, Park Tae Ho,
can't protect my own son...

51
00:02:50,380 --> 00:02:52,410
from Oh Jung Ran?

52
00:02:56,150 --> 00:02:58,850
If you're that worried about it,
fine.

53
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:02,750
I'll make things perfectly clear.

54
00:03:04,060 --> 00:03:05,920
Here. Put that suitcase away.

55
00:03:07,030 --> 00:03:08,030
Follow me.

56
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:18,140
Listen to me, and listen carefully.

57
00:03:18,740 --> 00:03:21,110
This nonsense
about getting Min Jun fired?

58
00:03:21,540 --> 00:03:22,910
Stop making trouble
and stay out of it.

59
00:03:23,370 --> 00:03:25,910
Tell Director Seo and the board
I said so.

60
00:03:26,810 --> 00:03:30,520
So you're keeping that amnesiac
in his position?

61
00:03:30,950 --> 00:03:31,950
What did I tell you?

62
00:03:33,250 --> 00:03:36,120
Ms. Oh will keep questioning
Min Jun's competence.

63
00:03:37,820 --> 00:03:40,220
Unlike her, I'm not your wife,

64
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:43,090
and I don't have the power
to sway the board.

65
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:47,000
There's no way for me
to protect Min Jun.

66
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:51,670
Please.
Just let me leave with Min Jun.

67
00:03:52,270 --> 00:03:53,270
Leave?

68
00:03:54,340 --> 00:03:56,540
What's this pathetic little act?

69
00:03:58,940 --> 00:03:59,980
Hold on.

70
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:02,180
So Kim Myung Hui threatens to leave,

71
00:04:02,250 --> 00:04:04,220
and suddenly you march in here
holding her hand...

72
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:06,650
to defend that brat?

73
00:04:06,650 --> 00:04:08,920
Did you call my son "that brat?"

74
00:04:09,620 --> 00:04:10,620
Watch your mouth!

75
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:14,060
Let me make myself clear.

76
00:04:14,660 --> 00:04:16,330
Don't you dare mess
with Min Jun again.

77
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:19,400
If you try to undermine
his position,

78
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:23,300
don't think your own position
as my wife is safe.

79
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:28,340
What does that mean?
Are you threatening to divorce me?

80
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:35,780
Don't think I won't.

81
00:04:37,650 --> 00:04:38,650
Honey.

82
00:04:39,150 --> 00:04:41,450
Both of you,
listen to me very carefully.

83
00:04:43,190 --> 00:04:45,660
From your children
to your positions,

84
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,790
I'm the one who decides everything.

85
00:04:48,130 --> 00:04:50,930
I'll do whatever is most beneficial
for Adele!

86
00:04:53,500 --> 00:04:55,370
Don't get arrogant...

87
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:00,910
and step out of line again.

88
00:05:01,610 --> 00:05:02,610
Understand?

89
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,980
Did you seriously pull
a crying act...

90
00:05:11,980 --> 00:05:14,020
where you packed a bag
and threatened to leave?

91
00:05:15,490 --> 00:05:17,390
When you're threatening
to kill my son,

92
00:05:18,390 --> 00:05:19,960
I'll do whatever it takes.

93
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:24,330
How long do you think
those crocodile tears will work?

94
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:28,200
At least I managed to sway
the chairman today.

95
00:05:29,670 --> 00:05:32,240
He held my hand,
brought me all the way here,

96
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:35,170
and warned you he could leave you.

97
00:05:36,370 --> 00:05:37,610
I thought I made myself clear.

98
00:05:38,540 --> 00:05:40,810
Park Tae Ho can never leave me.

99
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:44,820
We'll just have to see
about that, won't we?

100
00:05:46,150 --> 00:05:49,250
Who will the chairman abandon,

101
00:05:50,050 --> 00:05:51,920
you or me?

102
00:05:53,220 --> 00:05:54,230
I'm curious.

103
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,600
No.

104
00:06:02,230 --> 00:06:04,170
Park Tae Ho would never leave me.

105
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,270
For the last 30 years,

106
00:06:07,070 --> 00:06:09,940
I've been Park Tae Ho's wife
and the lady of Adele.

107
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,310
How could he throw
that all away now?

108
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:17,680
In the end, you're the one
who will be cast aside.

109
00:06:29,490 --> 00:06:30,600
So, it's come to this.

110
00:06:32,500 --> 00:06:33,500
I'm so sorry, Myung Hui.

111
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:37,570
Even though I took on your identity,

112
00:06:38,970 --> 00:06:42,240
I wanted to preserve
your legal status as a single woman.

113
00:06:44,580 --> 00:06:47,850
I wanted to spare you
the marriage you never wanted.

114
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,320
But now,

115
00:06:53,420 --> 00:06:55,120
I think I have to give up...

116
00:06:56,290 --> 00:06:58,060
even the last shred of my pride.

117
00:07:15,140 --> 00:07:17,910
For goodness' sake.
Why are you crying again?

118
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:20,340
I told you not to worry
about Min Jun.

119
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:23,280
Stop crying already.

120
00:07:23,780 --> 00:07:25,580
For the past 30 years,

121
00:07:25,850 --> 00:07:27,890
you always held back your tears
in front of me.

122
00:07:28,790 --> 00:07:30,690
Why have you gotten so fragile?

123
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,120
I'm...

124
00:07:33,220 --> 00:07:34,890
only human. And I'm a woman too.

125
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:39,630
I tried to be strong for so long,

126
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:43,030
but I guess
I've finally broken down.

127
00:07:44,870 --> 00:07:45,870
Unbelievable.

128
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:51,840
All right.

129
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,050
There.

130
00:07:56,610 --> 00:07:57,620
That's right.

131
00:07:58,450 --> 00:08:02,150
I have to give up every last shred
of my pride now.

132
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:05,920
I'll willingly walk
into the misery...

133
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:08,430
of becoming Park Tae Ho's wife...

134
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,060
to take everything
from Oh Jung Ran...

135
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:14,730
and protect Min Jun.

136
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:57,170
- Excuse me.
- Have we met before?

137
00:09:01,350 --> 00:09:03,350
I lost my memory in an accident,

138
00:09:04,050 --> 00:09:05,580
but I just had a strange feeling.

139
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:09,050
You seem really familiar
for some reason.

140
00:09:10,020 --> 00:09:11,790
Do you know me by any chance?

141
00:09:14,060 --> 00:09:16,490
No, I don't think I do.

142
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,830
Is that so?

143
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:24,840
Sorry, I must be mistaken.

144
00:09:35,910 --> 00:09:36,910
Chloe.

145
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:45,720
Chloe?

146
00:09:53,230 --> 00:09:54,900
What were you talking to him about?

147
00:09:55,670 --> 00:09:56,670
Don't tell me you...

148
00:09:57,700 --> 00:10:00,470
He said he lost his memory
in an accident too.

149
00:10:05,310 --> 00:10:06,340
Let's head back.

150
00:10:24,330 --> 00:10:25,930
So that woman is Chloe?

151
00:10:30,870 --> 00:10:35,170
Is that why she seemed so familiar?
Because Hyun Jun knows her?

152
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,150
Chloe...

153
00:10:44,620 --> 00:10:46,420
Why am I bothered by her?

154
00:10:48,250 --> 00:10:50,050
Did she really lose her memory?

155
00:10:51,060 --> 00:10:52,360
What if she's lying?

156
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:56,860
I need to find out for sure.

157
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,260
(Adele)

158
00:10:59,500 --> 00:11:00,830
(Proposal Issued by the Board)

159
00:11:06,170 --> 00:11:09,970
Handle those malicious articles
about Director Park Min Jun.

160
00:11:10,210 --> 00:11:11,510
Make them disappear.

161
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:13,110
But sir...

162
00:11:13,110 --> 00:11:15,510
Then would you rather be dismissed
in my son's place,

163
00:11:16,010 --> 00:11:17,250
Director Seo?

164
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:18,880
Of course not, sir.

165
00:11:19,420 --> 00:11:21,490
I will do as you wish.

166
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,120
Here.

167
00:11:32,260 --> 00:11:33,330
Now,

168
00:11:34,230 --> 00:11:35,770
are you satisfied?

169
00:11:43,570 --> 00:11:45,740
What? A divorce?

170
00:11:46,880 --> 00:11:49,750
What if you do get them to divorce?
Then what?

171
00:11:50,580 --> 00:11:52,150
Wait, don't tell me...

172
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:55,920
you're actually planning
to marry Chairman Park.

173
00:11:57,560 --> 00:12:00,460
It's the only way
to crush Oh Jung Ran...

174
00:12:01,230 --> 00:12:03,490
and make Min Jun the successor.

175
00:12:04,030 --> 00:12:05,060
But...

176
00:12:05,230 --> 00:12:06,800
For the past 30 years,

177
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:10,100
I've put up with everything
to make him the successor.

178
00:12:12,140 --> 00:12:14,170
I used to think
protecting Min Jun...

179
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:17,540
was more important
than crushing Oh Jung Ran.

180
00:12:18,510 --> 00:12:19,610
But...

181
00:12:19,910 --> 00:12:22,480
if Oh Jung Ran is trying
to kill Min Jun,

182
00:12:23,450 --> 00:12:24,980
then I have to fight back.

183
00:12:25,950 --> 00:12:28,220
I'll take everything she has...

184
00:12:29,290 --> 00:12:31,420
and erase her from Min Jun's life.

185
00:12:37,930 --> 00:12:39,000
Come on.

186
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:43,330
I just secured Min Jun's position.
Why the long face?

187
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:48,310
The most important issue
still hasn't been resolved.

188
00:12:50,170 --> 00:12:55,110
We have to find who targeted Min Jun
and caused his amnesia.

189
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:57,450
Don't worry about that.

190
00:12:57,450 --> 00:13:00,990
I ordered a thorough investigation,
and I'm personally overseeing it.

191
00:13:01,190 --> 00:13:04,020
Even so, I can't just sit back
and do nothing.

192
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:08,460
I need to know exactly why Min Jun
and Chloe had that accident there...

193
00:13:09,130 --> 00:13:14,270
and the details of what happened
at the warehouse that day.

194
00:13:15,130 --> 00:13:18,670
You were there too, sir,
so please tell me what happened.

195
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,910
Well, I...

196
00:13:24,540 --> 00:13:26,840
There's not much to tell.

197
00:13:27,180 --> 00:13:30,750
I was just inspecting the warehouse.
That's it.

198
00:13:31,980 --> 00:13:35,790
Just let the police handle it.
You focus...

199
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:39,220
on the deal with Assemblyman Kwon.

200
00:13:41,590 --> 00:13:44,600
The day we're supposed
to pay Assemblyman Kwon...

201
00:13:45,330 --> 00:13:46,760
is almost here.

202
00:13:48,070 --> 00:13:50,530
Yes, sir. Understood.

203
00:13:57,270 --> 00:14:00,110
He's hiding
what happened at the warehouse.

204
00:14:01,380 --> 00:14:04,550
Something happened there
that he wants kept secret.

205
00:14:06,580 --> 00:14:10,750
I need to know what it is
to prove Oh Jung Ran's crime.

206
00:14:23,970 --> 00:14:27,670
What happened at the warehouse
on the day of the accident?

207
00:14:29,710 --> 00:14:30,710
What?

208
00:14:32,710 --> 00:14:33,710
Right.

209
00:14:34,380 --> 00:14:36,480
Ms. Choi must know something.

210
00:14:40,380 --> 00:14:42,090
You're back together with Min Jun...

211
00:14:42,820 --> 00:14:47,160
while keeping him in the dark
about everything that's happened?

212
00:14:48,690 --> 00:14:50,590
Is that really
what Kim Myung Hui decided?

213
00:14:50,730 --> 00:14:53,730
It's because Min Jun is struggling
to get his memory back.

214
00:14:54,330 --> 00:14:57,170
As a result,
he's relying on me a lot.

215
00:14:58,800 --> 00:14:59,940
Even so,

216
00:15:00,700 --> 00:15:03,470
I doubt she intends
for you two to get married.

217
00:15:04,010 --> 00:15:07,010
It could happen
if I win his heart, right?

218
00:15:07,380 --> 00:15:10,650
Please, just give me your permission
to get back together with him.

219
00:15:15,050 --> 00:15:17,760
I'll let it slide
since you say Min Jun needs you.

220
00:15:18,460 --> 00:15:21,830
But if you get cocky like before,

221
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:23,490
you'll regret it.

222
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:27,500
Of course. I've learned my lesson.

223
00:15:28,730 --> 00:15:30,200
And one more thing...

224
00:15:30,930 --> 00:15:32,340
It's about Chloe.

225
00:15:34,670 --> 00:15:35,740
Chloe? What about her?

226
00:15:36,870 --> 00:15:39,880
I ran into her at the hospital,
and something seemed off.

227
00:15:40,610 --> 00:15:42,510
She called the police
and questioned me...

228
00:15:42,510 --> 00:15:44,420
about the incident at the warehouse.

229
00:15:44,920 --> 00:15:47,350
It makes me doubt
she really lost her memory.

230
00:15:49,190 --> 00:15:50,890
She called the police?

231
00:15:57,390 --> 00:16:00,000
The termination of Chloe's contract
has been processed.

232
00:16:00,660 --> 00:16:02,870
All we need is her signature.

233
00:16:02,900 --> 00:16:04,100
Right.

234
00:16:04,800 --> 00:16:07,940
If her contract is terminated,
that means she's fired, right?

235
00:16:08,510 --> 00:16:10,770
Since the marriage is off,
wouldn't that...

236
00:16:11,780 --> 00:16:13,610
cancel the competition?

237
00:16:14,180 --> 00:16:15,510
Then I can get my job back...

238
00:16:15,510 --> 00:16:16,580
Choi Yu Na.

239
00:16:18,950 --> 00:16:20,580
You're still as greedy as ever.

240
00:16:21,990 --> 00:16:25,120
Just quietly take care
of Min Jun for now.

241
00:16:26,490 --> 00:16:27,490
Yes, sir.

242
00:16:32,730 --> 00:16:33,930
What's going on?

243
00:16:35,570 --> 00:16:36,570
Leave it there.

244
00:16:37,800 --> 00:16:39,370
(Consultant, Chloe Lee)

245
00:16:41,070 --> 00:16:44,510
Take this to Chloe
and end things with her.

246
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:46,710
Father!

247
00:16:46,710 --> 00:16:50,080
End our contract with her
and call off...

248
00:16:50,950 --> 00:16:52,180
the marriage arrangement.

249
00:16:52,950 --> 00:16:54,020
Got it?

250
00:17:03,830 --> 00:17:04,830
What do you think you're doing?

251
00:17:05,300 --> 00:17:07,830
You must be doing this
because Chloe lost her memory,

252
00:17:08,970 --> 00:17:12,670
but you kept Min Jun in his position
when the same thing happened to him.

253
00:17:13,540 --> 00:17:16,170
Is Chloe the same as my son?

254
00:17:16,370 --> 00:17:18,380
She's with me, your other son!

255
00:17:19,710 --> 00:17:21,210
She's the woman I love.

256
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:29,620
You already gave us
your permission to marry.

257
00:17:30,420 --> 00:17:31,490
Chloe's memory loss?

258
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:35,090
It doesn't matter to me.

259
00:17:36,830 --> 00:17:38,430
Once she's out of the hospital
and stable,

260
00:17:39,760 --> 00:17:40,930
we're getting married.

261
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:48,240
You may not be as capable
as Min Jun in the office,

262
00:17:48,310 --> 00:17:51,510
but I thought you at least knew
how the world works.

263
00:17:52,140 --> 00:17:57,180
But not only are you incompetent,
you're letting love blind you too.

264
00:17:58,620 --> 00:17:59,750
As for Chloe,

265
00:18:00,280 --> 00:18:03,820
I'm cutting her off from both
my company and my family for good.

266
00:18:05,420 --> 00:18:07,320
You'd better give up on her
and your feelings...

267
00:18:09,030 --> 00:18:10,390
before I get rid of you too.

268
00:18:14,970 --> 00:18:15,970
Father...

269
00:18:35,750 --> 00:18:37,690
Why did you want to see me?

270
00:18:40,860 --> 00:18:41,860
You still...

271
00:18:42,490 --> 00:18:44,500
haven't given me an answer,
Ms. Choi.

272
00:18:45,760 --> 00:18:49,870
You never told me
what happened at the warehouse.

273
00:18:51,270 --> 00:18:52,270
That's...

274
00:18:52,340 --> 00:18:55,070
If you're too afraid
of the chairman to answer,

275
00:18:55,370 --> 00:18:57,010
you're free to go.

276
00:18:57,370 --> 00:19:00,910
I'll assume
you're one of his people,

277
00:19:02,050 --> 00:19:05,450
that you'll never stand on my side,

278
00:19:05,780 --> 00:19:07,920
and that I can never accept you...

279
00:19:08,390 --> 00:19:10,020
for my son.

280
00:19:12,890 --> 00:19:13,990
If I answer you,

281
00:19:14,460 --> 00:19:16,560
does that mean I can stay
by Min Jun's side?

282
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:22,730
Only until Min Jun gets
his memory back.

283
00:19:24,500 --> 00:19:26,470
I'll give you until then.

284
00:19:26,670 --> 00:19:27,740
Of course,

285
00:19:28,270 --> 00:19:31,780
once his memory returns,
it'll be his decision.

286
00:19:32,010 --> 00:19:34,980
So if his memory doesn't come back,
I get to stay?

287
00:19:35,950 --> 00:19:37,750
And if he still wants me
after he gets his memory back,

288
00:19:37,850 --> 00:19:39,550
you won't object.

289
00:19:39,950 --> 00:19:41,550
Regardless of his memory,

290
00:19:42,250 --> 00:19:44,820
Min Jun could still reject you.

291
00:19:45,860 --> 00:19:48,260
That part's up to me, isn't it?

292
00:19:50,730 --> 00:19:53,500
Then, are you ready to answer?

293
00:19:54,730 --> 00:19:55,730
That's right.

294
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:58,300
Park Min Jun is the only card
I have left to play.

295
00:19:59,240 --> 00:20:00,640
Instead of Chairman Park,

296
00:20:00,940 --> 00:20:03,440
I need President Kim on my side.

297
00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:07,310
That day, at the warehouse,

298
00:20:08,510 --> 00:20:10,710
the chairman tried to kill Chloe.

299
00:20:13,420 --> 00:20:16,550
Mind you, she was trying
to kill him too.

300
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:19,120
What did you just say?

301
00:20:20,260 --> 00:20:21,330
What on earth...

302
00:20:21,990 --> 00:20:25,500
Chloe came to Adele from the start
with her eyes on the bio division.

303
00:20:26,030 --> 00:20:28,830
She planned to harm the chairman
to achieve her goal.

304
00:20:29,870 --> 00:20:32,700
I figured out her plan
and informed the chairman.

305
00:20:33,940 --> 00:20:35,910
How could she...

306
00:20:37,710 --> 00:20:40,840
What about Oh Jung Ran, then?

307
00:20:41,380 --> 00:20:42,910
Did she know about this?

308
00:20:44,110 --> 00:20:45,120
Yes.

309
00:20:45,820 --> 00:20:48,750
She knew everything from the start.

310
00:20:51,690 --> 00:20:53,890
The chairman and Chloe
were trying to kill each other,

311
00:20:55,030 --> 00:20:57,390
and Oh Jung Ran knew
about the chairman's plan.

312
00:20:58,500 --> 00:21:00,230
I was right all along.

313
00:21:01,030 --> 00:21:03,500
She sent Min Jun there on purpose.

314
00:21:04,100 --> 00:21:06,540
She knew the area would be cleared
of security cameras,

315
00:21:07,040 --> 00:21:09,270
which meant
there'd be no evidence of her crime.

316
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:18,620
It was handed to me on a platter,
and I failed.

317
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:21,390
This is so frustrating.

318
00:21:22,050 --> 00:21:24,250
I'm so furious I can't stand it.

319
00:21:28,490 --> 00:21:32,700
Park Tae Ho's still protecting Min Jun
even though he has amnesia?

320
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:36,200
What if this has nothing to do
with Kim Myung Hui's tearful act,

321
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:39,940
and he really intends to make
that punk his successor?

322
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:47,680
No. If Hyun Jun is going
to inherit Adele,

323
00:21:49,310 --> 00:21:51,650
then Park Min Jun has to die.

324
00:21:52,180 --> 00:21:53,980
Somehow, I need to try again.

325
00:21:54,790 --> 00:21:56,150
There you go again.

326
00:21:57,350 --> 00:21:59,620
Thinking dangerous thoughts, are we?

327
00:22:00,790 --> 00:22:03,560
Leave Mr. Min Jun alone.

328
00:22:04,830 --> 00:22:07,100
What's that supposed to mean?

329
00:22:07,260 --> 00:22:09,870
I know all about the conversation...

330
00:22:10,230 --> 00:22:14,000
you had with Mr. Min Jun
the day he got into that accident.

331
00:22:14,340 --> 00:22:16,840
Wait, what?

332
00:22:17,010 --> 00:22:20,040
If anything else happens to him,

333
00:22:22,080 --> 00:22:25,480
I'll tell the chairman everything.

334
00:22:27,550 --> 00:22:28,850
Mrs. Ok.

335
00:22:29,350 --> 00:22:30,350
Yes, ma'am.

336
00:22:31,220 --> 00:22:34,860
Remember, I'm always watching you.

337
00:22:35,430 --> 00:22:38,560
But don't be too scared.

338
00:22:39,060 --> 00:22:40,930
If you behave yourself,

339
00:22:41,230 --> 00:22:43,970
I'll stay out of your way.

340
00:23:02,150 --> 00:23:05,690
Oh Jung Ran will lay low
for a while.

341
00:23:06,120 --> 00:23:07,590
The job is important,

342
00:23:08,090 --> 00:23:10,290
but we can't let people get killed.

343
00:23:21,610 --> 00:23:23,640
If Tae Ho finds out,
I'm in deep trouble.

344
00:23:24,780 --> 00:23:27,880
He won't believe any excuse I make.

345
00:23:27,940 --> 00:23:32,220
So basically,
Butler Ok has you by the throat.

346
00:23:32,280 --> 00:23:35,620
How do I shut her up? No, wait.

347
00:23:35,690 --> 00:23:38,320
I have to kick her
out of this house.

348
00:23:38,960 --> 00:23:42,090
How much would it take
to make her shut up and leave?

349
00:23:42,430 --> 00:23:44,090
Money won't work on her.

350
00:23:44,760 --> 00:23:48,700
In over ten years, I've never
seen her obsess over money.

351
00:23:48,770 --> 00:23:50,870
Then what am I supposed to do?

352
00:23:52,200 --> 00:23:55,710
Didn't she say she'd leave you alone
if you behaved?

353
00:23:56,110 --> 00:23:58,310
For now, just lay low.

354
00:23:58,380 --> 00:24:00,480
How am I supposed to do that
in this situation?

355
00:24:00,540 --> 00:24:03,980
It's not like you have
any other options.

356
00:24:05,780 --> 00:24:07,120
- I'm getting a headache.
- Oh dear.

357
00:24:13,020 --> 00:24:15,860
Oh Jung Ran. I'll never forgive her.

358
00:24:16,290 --> 00:24:20,030
Somehow, I have to prove
that she tried to kill Min Jun.

359
00:24:20,500 --> 00:24:23,830
I checked with the police,
but the investigation has stalled.

360
00:24:25,100 --> 00:24:26,700
What about Min Jun's dashcam?

361
00:24:26,700 --> 00:24:28,070
That was already looked into,

362
00:24:28,470 --> 00:24:31,780
but all it shows is him
leaving the house.

363
00:24:33,540 --> 00:24:37,350
Oh Jung Ran sent him there
from the house.

364
00:24:38,110 --> 00:24:40,050
But she has a solid alibi.

365
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:42,820
I met with the spa employees again,

366
00:24:43,350 --> 00:24:44,890
and it looks like
they coordinated their stories.

367
00:24:45,060 --> 00:24:46,760
With the help of her driver,

368
00:24:47,420 --> 00:24:49,090
she planned it out perfectly.

369
00:24:49,590 --> 00:24:50,890
Tell me about it.

370
00:24:51,730 --> 00:24:54,600
This is what I gathered
from tailing him.

371
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:56,770
He may look like a slacker,

372
00:24:56,900 --> 00:24:58,600
but he's meticulous
about the work she gives him.

373
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:00,640
Mr. Song...

374
00:25:01,910 --> 00:25:05,080
From the day my sister died
until now,

375
00:25:05,410 --> 00:25:08,080
he's always been
by Oh Jung Ran's side,

376
00:25:09,010 --> 00:25:12,620
just like you and Woo Jin
have always been by mine.

377
00:25:14,280 --> 00:25:15,290
So?

378
00:25:15,790 --> 00:25:18,560
I need to do some digging on him.

379
00:25:19,590 --> 00:25:22,160
Look into his history
with Oh Jung Ran.

380
00:25:32,740 --> 00:25:35,870
I'm sorry
things turned out this way.

381
00:25:38,940 --> 00:25:41,540
I'm sorry to you as well, sir.

382
00:25:42,410 --> 00:25:43,410
It's fine.

383
00:25:45,050 --> 00:25:47,820
With her memory gone,
she can't be expected to work.

384
00:25:48,750 --> 00:25:49,990
This was bound to happen.

385
00:25:51,590 --> 00:25:55,030
Why assume she can't?
With Chloe's talent,

386
00:25:55,090 --> 00:25:57,160
she'll learn the ropes in no time.

387
00:25:58,160 --> 00:26:00,060
Don't agree to terminate
the contract.

388
00:26:00,560 --> 00:26:01,900
Just ask them for more time.

389
00:26:02,100 --> 00:26:03,130
No.

390
00:26:04,630 --> 00:26:08,200
As soon as Chloe is discharged,
we're going back to the US.

391
00:26:09,010 --> 00:26:12,240
I plan on wrapping up
all of our affairs here.

392
00:26:33,300 --> 00:26:34,860
It doesn't look like...

393
00:26:34,860 --> 00:26:37,000
Director Hyun Jun
will give up so easily.

394
00:26:38,740 --> 00:26:39,770
What about Chloe?

395
00:26:39,840 --> 00:26:42,140
It seems
she'll accept the termination,

396
00:26:42,840 --> 00:26:45,540
but whether she actually
lost her memory or is faking it...

397
00:26:46,140 --> 00:26:47,210
remains unclear.

398
00:26:47,810 --> 00:26:49,280
I see.

399
00:26:51,210 --> 00:26:54,120
Have Chloe come
to the office tomorrow.

400
00:26:56,290 --> 00:26:58,050
Isn't she passing by here today?

401
00:27:06,230 --> 00:27:08,030
I wanted to ask her
about Hyun Jun...

402
00:27:08,030 --> 00:27:10,830
and whether
she genuinely doesn't remember me.

403
00:27:12,740 --> 00:27:13,740
Chloe.

404
00:27:15,710 --> 00:27:17,540
Chloe...

405
00:27:19,340 --> 00:27:22,150
Why can't I get her and her name
out of my head?

406
00:27:31,350 --> 00:27:33,320
Hey, Hyun Jun.

407
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:41,330
You saw Chloe?

408
00:27:41,830 --> 00:27:44,770
Yes. I happened
to run into her here.

409
00:27:46,370 --> 00:27:47,370
But...

410
00:27:47,740 --> 00:27:49,940
something about her and her name
feels familiar.

411
00:27:51,340 --> 00:27:52,980
Is it because
she's someone you know?

412
00:27:56,250 --> 00:27:59,880
You cared for her
when she had that fit outside my room.

413
00:28:01,380 --> 00:28:03,890
Are you two close?
How do you know her?

414
00:28:04,120 --> 00:28:05,360
I like her...

415
00:28:07,820 --> 00:28:09,160
She's the woman I love.

416
00:28:13,430 --> 00:28:14,430
Really?

417
00:28:20,970 --> 00:28:22,040
Then what about me?

418
00:28:24,270 --> 00:28:25,280
What?

419
00:28:26,810 --> 00:28:28,450
Did I know her?

420
00:28:29,680 --> 00:28:34,020
She says she doesn't know me,
but I feel I must've known her.

421
00:28:36,050 --> 00:28:37,290
What were we...

422
00:28:38,320 --> 00:28:39,890
to each other?

423
00:28:42,360 --> 00:28:44,230
Didn't Chloe tell you
that you were strangers?

424
00:28:45,630 --> 00:28:47,030
Then you're strangers, I guess.

425
00:28:52,240 --> 00:28:53,240
Go on inside.

426
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:56,070
I'll get going.

427
00:29:02,080 --> 00:29:03,210
Chloe...

428
00:29:05,120 --> 00:29:06,650
We're strangers?

429
00:29:15,060 --> 00:29:16,060
Oh dear.

430
00:29:17,130 --> 00:29:19,700
You haven't even been discharged.
Was this really necessary?

431
00:29:19,930 --> 00:29:22,730
You told me they wanted to talk
about the accident.

432
00:29:23,470 --> 00:29:26,640
I'm curious about
what happened that day too.

433
00:29:27,140 --> 00:29:30,710
If you start feeling unwell at all,
you have to tell me immediately.

434
00:29:30,940 --> 00:29:32,580
Okay. Don't worry.

435
00:29:33,940 --> 00:29:35,980
The chairman's office is this way.
Let's go.

436
00:29:48,490 --> 00:29:51,260
Now that we're all here,
please tell us.

437
00:29:52,800 --> 00:29:55,370
What happened
at the warehouse that day?

438
00:29:58,640 --> 00:30:02,010
What happened that day
at the warehouse...

439
00:30:04,470 --> 00:30:05,940
was a serious crime.

440
00:30:07,210 --> 00:30:08,280
A crime?

441
00:30:08,310 --> 00:30:10,380
Chloe was about
to sell trade secrets...

442
00:30:14,020 --> 00:30:16,490
to a rival company.

443
00:30:18,860 --> 00:30:19,860
What on earth...

444
00:30:26,930 --> 00:30:29,430
If you hadn't lost your memory,

445
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:32,240
you'd surely find
this situation unfair.

446
00:30:33,600 --> 00:30:35,370
Go on, deny it.

447
00:30:46,920 --> 00:30:49,090
Jung Ran, please.

448
00:30:50,120 --> 00:30:51,820
That's enough.

449
00:30:52,260 --> 00:30:55,190
You can't just skip meals
and keep drinking like this.

450
00:30:56,290 --> 00:30:59,100
I have to drink...

451
00:30:59,830 --> 00:31:02,330
just to feel like I can breathe.

452
00:31:02,730 --> 00:31:04,630
You're usually as tough as nails,

453
00:31:05,170 --> 00:31:08,540
so why do you sound so defeated?
It hurts to hear that.

454
00:31:10,070 --> 00:31:12,080
I'm the one who's upset here.

455
00:31:13,080 --> 00:31:14,980
That monster, Park Tae Ho,

456
00:31:15,810 --> 00:31:19,280
is threatening to toss me aside
after using me.

457
00:31:20,650 --> 00:31:23,890
My son, my precious boy,

458
00:31:25,620 --> 00:31:27,320
can't even stand the sight of me.

459
00:31:28,560 --> 00:31:30,160
And that witch, Kim Myung Hui,

460
00:31:30,790 --> 00:31:34,000
is out for my blood.

461
00:31:35,500 --> 00:31:37,170
And now, to top it all off,

462
00:31:37,430 --> 00:31:41,000
even Butler Ok looks down on me.

463
00:31:45,280 --> 00:31:47,480
I feel like I'm suffocating.

464
00:31:48,440 --> 00:31:50,950
I don't know what else to do.

465
00:32:14,970 --> 00:32:15,970
Song Geun Tae.

466
00:32:17,010 --> 00:32:18,740
Oh Jung Ran's right-hand man.

467
00:32:19,810 --> 00:32:23,350
He's the card I'll play to make
Oh Jung Ran and Park Tae Ho divorce.

468
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:50,170
(Pearl in Red)

469
00:32:50,510 --> 00:32:52,680
Stop tormenting me
and just spit it out.

470
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:53,810
What do you want from me?

471
00:32:53,980 --> 00:32:55,350
Is it money? How much?

472
00:32:55,610 --> 00:32:57,250
Name your price
to keep quiet and leave.

473
00:32:57,580 --> 00:32:59,550
If you really want Ms. Oh
for yourself,

474
00:32:59,950 --> 00:33:01,820
then reveal the truth
about that day.

475
00:33:02,020 --> 00:33:04,550
Bring me proof.

476
00:33:05,020 --> 00:33:08,160
I'll leave before you get the chance
to throw me out, Father.

477
00:33:08,390 --> 00:33:09,390
Son!

478
00:33:09,460 --> 00:33:12,660
I'll marry Chloe
and leave for the US with her.

479
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:15,200
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
